LCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cueW91dHViZS5jb20vd2F0Y2g_dj01QThHVVV1RjBHdyIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZjU4NDNhNTAtMWMxMS00OWVlLWJmODYtMmZhNWQ0MjE5NDQwIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAQ3cdvDXx-m2EhFSHoP-GfXXWWyMD1U-yH8n866r7C2f&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5A8GUUuF0Gw">官方</a>最大刷新率 144Hz） 。除此之外， <a data-i13n="cpos:32;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3VzLmNvbW11bml0eS5zYW1zdW5nLmNvbS90NS80Sy04Sy1hbmQtT3RoZXItVFZzL1M5NUItMTQyMC05LWlzc3Vlcy10aGF0LW5lZWQtYWRkcmVzc2luZy90ZC1wLzI0NzI4NzUiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImY1ODQzYTUwLTFjMTEtNDllZS1iZjg2LTJmYTVkNDIxOTQ0MCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAafHz4s4nRyeVXnYHLDCJQXtzJOWSib0AODXfNzD0T1e&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fus.community.samsung.com%2Ft5%2F4K-8K-and-Other-TVs%2FS95B-1420-9-issues-that-need-addressing%2Ftd-p%2F2472875">一些 S95B</a> <a data-i13n="cpos:33;pos:1" href="https://www.rtings.com/tv/discussions/I6IKUBFqpNRVtr9O/gamers-beware-of-1420-update-game-mode-hdr-hgig-dim">用户</a>抱怨最近固件更新后电视在“游戏模式”下的图像质量问题。这不应该让 S95B 与一台差劲的电视相媲美，而且如果你在明亮的房间里玩，它仍然是值得的。但随着更新型号即将推出，我们对于是否推荐它而不是专门用于游戏的 LG C2 有点犹豫。</p><h2>索尼A95K OLED</h2><p><core-commerce id="eb89fed88e1646c2bd89d0a5b9635c3f" data-type="product-list"></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:34;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlSOTVZUDM2P3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLXAwLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJmNTg0M2E1MC0xYzExLTQ5ZWUtYmY4Ni0yZmE1ZDQyMTk0NDAifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAVozk9MqJ1reWB6bmfRnwcOHeOy0JQuyg-UoSATj9OyE&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09R95YP36">索尼的 A95K</a>是另一款备受好评的 QD-OLED 电视，并且支持杜比视界。不过，它不支持 HDR10+，并且只有两个完整的 HDMI 2.1 端口。它也比 C2 或 S95B 贵得多，截至撰写本文时，55 英寸型号的起价为 2,300 美元。 <a data-i13n="cpos:35;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sony-2023-bravia-xr-tv-hands-on-bigger-brighter-and-even-better-looking-150030819.html">即将推出的 A95L</a>值得关注，因为它将是第一款支持 4K 120Hz 杜比视界的电视。</p><h2>三星QN90B</h2><p><core-commerce id="6d90fd701bdc4a32a67da33ab8a09319" data-type="product-list"></p><p>如果您更喜欢液晶电视的额外亮度，或者您认为您可能玩一款游戏（非常）长时间而担心<a data-i13n="cpos:36;pos:1" href="https://www.cnet.com/tech/home-entertainment/oled-screen-burn-in-rare-could-still-ruin-tv-nintendo-switch/">烧屏</a>，请考虑<a data-i13n="cpos:37;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Samsung Electronics;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=f85e63cd-e13c-4f9d-991c-9fbaadede3ac&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Samsung+Electronics&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAARGnOnQ1vSlqvY41-tZeI-nyN5TbicjjYfC0HZtAn8Rz&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.samsung.com%2Fus%2Ftelevisions-home-theater%2Ftvs%2Fsamsung-neo-qled-4k%2F55-class-qn90b-samsung-neo-qled-4k-smart-tv-2022-qn55qn90bafxza%2F">三星的 QN90B</a> 。它无法与优质 OLED 电视的对比度、响应时间或视角相媲美，但其 Mini LED 背光和量子点颜色应该能够比大多数 LCD 电视提供更丰富的图像，尤其是在 HDR 方面。它的运动和输入延迟也不应该引起问题，而且它可以比上面的模型更亮。与其他三星电视一样，它不支持杜比视界，但有四个完整的 HDMI 2.1 端口、ALLM 和所有主要 VRR 格式。它还具有多种尺寸，其中<a data-i13n="cpos:38;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Samsung Electronics;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=f85e63cd-e13c-4f9d-991c-9fbaadede3ac&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Samsung+Electronics&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAbA_68DTN3i0YsTFoGpFALlVjhPwcCJ4iyHwcDwVCE49&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.samsung.com%2Fus%2Ftelevisions-home-theater%2Ftvs%2Fsamsung-neo-qled-4k%2F43-class-qn90b-samsung-neo-qled-4k-smart-tv-2022-qn43qn90bafxza%2F">43 英寸</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:39;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Samsung Electronics;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=f85e63cd-e13c-4f9d-991c-9fbaadede3ac&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Samsung+Electronics&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAZ_ZLgXJ5k8CIzSkD-oY2AmVjTq9LFyq4e5XMCC54Dcs&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.samsung.com%2Fus%2Ftelevisions-home-theater%2Ftvs%2Fsamsung-neo-qled-4k%2F50-class-qn90b-samsung-neo-qled-4k-smart-tv-2022-qn50qn90bafxza%2F">50 英寸</a>型号能够达到 144Hz 刷新率。其余的最高可达 120Hz，这是 PS5 或 Xbox Series X/S 的最大值。</p><h2> TCL 6系列</h2><p><core-commerce id="816825c590c84655a60b82d630b83bfc" data-type="product-list"></p><p>不过，QN90B 并不便宜。对于预算紧张的人来说， <a data-i13n="cpos:40;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0IwQjdaWEdDVlk_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tcDAtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImY1ODQzYTUwLTFjMTEtNDllZS1iZjg2LTJmYTVkNDIxOTQ0MCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAc3vlyi6-ptVq6AyWc4dEFi200ohBfYqQKTaOZbCDEU1&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0B7ZXGCVY">TCL 的 6 系列 (R655) 电视</a>应该不错。它比 QN90B 有所下降，特别是在 HDR 性能和视角方面，但它在任何环境下都应该看起来不错，输入延迟低，支持所有主要 HDR 和 VRR 技术，以及 144Hz 刷新率。不过，它只有两个完整的 HDMI 2.1 端口。请注意，这是 Roku 电视 - 如果您更喜欢 Google 的 TV 操作系统， <a data-i13n="cpos:41;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0IwQjVZWk5aVFo_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tcDAtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImY1ODQzYTUwLTFjMTEtNDllZS1iZjg2LTJmYTVkNDIxOTQ0MCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAfSfmQbSFLg_Flv72Kf5qSKWdeBVewsQFHYJZd6X4FOQ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0B5YZNZTZ">海信的 U8H</a>是同等价格的有力竞争对手。</p><h2>维齐奥MQX</h2><p><core-commerce id="a0d2ae1992e7418c8ff8cf81acfd3940" data-type="product-list"></p><p>另一方面， <a data-i13n="cpos:42;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlWQ1pDUjFXP3RoPTEmdGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tcDAtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImY1ODQzYTUwLTFjMTEtNDllZS1iZjg2LTJmYTVkNDIxOTQ0MCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAZG1xD_8JObOoYjYN7U9Tpj7xW3-nWdFo1u_OSHAG-OX&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09VCZCR1W%3Fth%3D1">Vizio 的 M 系列 Quantum X</a>看起来不太好，但对于帧速率迷来说，它支持 120Hz 刷新率，其 50 英寸型号能够达到 240Hz，尽管分辨率为 1080p。对于想要玩<em>《反恐精英》</em>等竞技射击游戏的 PC 游戏玩家来说，在这个价格范围内，它是一个大显示屏的例外。</p><h2> TCL 5系列</h2><p><core-commerce id="155852d5cbaf41daaa5c448ba4d9be08" data-type="product-list"></p><p>在低端市场， <a data-i13n="cpos:43;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9UQ0wtQ2xhc3MtRG9sYnktVmlzaW9uLUZyZWVTeW5jL2RwL0IwQjgxRFZRTks_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tcDAtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImY1ODQzYTUwLTFjMTEtNDllZS1iZjg2LTJmYTVkNDIxOTQ0MCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAb2ghNl4HPWgQvVXpipUgAbG_Hq-JRI-Udg7QaSPUdU8&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FTCL-Class-Dolby-Vision-FreeSync%2Fdp%2FB0B81DVQNK">TCL 的 5 系列 (S555)</a>是一款评价很高的 QLED 电视，具有低延迟、HDR、局部调光和比该系列中大多数型号更好的对比度。它在技术上也支持 VRR，但与许多更便宜的电视一样，它的刷新率仅限于 60Hz，并且缺乏 HDMI 2.1。</p><p><em>理查德·劳勒为本报告做出了贡献。</em></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/best-tvs-for-gaming-180033983.html?src=rss]]>;</description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-tvs-for-gaming-180033983.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> f5843a50-1c11-49ee-bf86-2fa5d4219440</guid><dc:creator>杰夫·邓恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 22 Jun 2023 20:00:09 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687464010</ingested><modified> 2023-06-22T20:00:22+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Video Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jeff Dunn]]></category><media:content height="4584" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-02/eedba4b0-76cc-11eb-aff7-b3bb49e900d8" width="8149"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="4584" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-02/eedba4b0-76cc-11eb-aff7-b3bb49e900d8" width="8149"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Future Publishing via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Living room with Microsoft Xbox S