-generate-custom-templates-in-sheets-185527176.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/googles-duet-ai-can-generate-custom-templates-in-sheets-185527176.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 04eb6b98-bd36-49b8-8c93-133ff39387c8</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 22 Jun 2023 18:55:27 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687460146</ingested><modified> 2023-06-22T18:55:48+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="4523" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-12/07bfc550-71ae-11ed-8feb-d9a461d9371d" width="6781"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="4523" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-12/07bfc550-71ae-11ed-8feb-d9a461d9371d" width="6781"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[NurPhoto via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Google neon is seen during the reopening of Google office in a historical building at the Main Square in Krakow, Poland on November 29, 2022. After nearly seven years of absence, Google reopened in Krakow hiring engineers which together with hub in Warsaw will create the largest center in Europe dealing with Google Cloud computing services. (Photo by Beata Zawrzel/NurPhoto via Getty Images)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Google Opens Cloud Hub In Krakow, Poland]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best iPhone accessories for 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>新的 Apple iPhone 14 用户应该在拆箱后不久就考虑一下他们想要的新手机配件。与去年的 iPhone 13s 一样，今年的型号没有配备交流电源适配器，因此您可能需要准备一个东西。如果您打算全面采用无线充电，您可以利用最好的 MagSafe 技术以及众多配件可供选择。我们测试了一些最好的 iPhone 配件，从 Apple AirTag 到无线耳机再到手机壳，并在这里收集了最好的配件。</p><h2>苹果 MagSafe 无线充电器</h2><p><core-commerce id="17be105c44f44e2c924fc9778cb6b892" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>苹果第一方配件通常有更好、更便宜的替代品，但如果你有新 iPhone，该公司的<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9BcHBsZS1NSFhIM0FNLUEtTWFnU2FmZS1DaGFyZ2VyL2RwL0IwOEw1TlA2Tkc_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZWEtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjYyN2FmM2ZkLTU5NGItMzE3OS04YzEzLWJhZGYzOTQwOTBjMCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAaRxUzZ1Mh5KMgSPjBoTccOKa-8hj3LtggM_hnahkFeW&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-MHXH3AM-A-MagSafe-Charger%2Fdp%2FB08L5NP6NG">MagSafe 无线充电器</a>值得考虑。与所有其他 MagSafe 配件一样，这款充电板使用磁铁吸附在最新 iPhone 的背面，而且非常坚固。您不仅可以安全地拿起手机并在磁盘仍然连接的情况下使用它，而且 iPhone 还可以通过充电器的电线悬挂而不会掉落。 （你可能仍然不应该这样做。）</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>充电板本身大约有四分之一英寸厚，因此几乎不会给 iPhone 增加任何重量。磁铁只能吸附在最新的 iPhone 上，但它仍然可以为旧型号无线充电，回到 iPhone 8。我只希望电缆长于三英尺，这样你就有更多的余地在沙发上或室内使用 iPhone。睡觉时打开电源。</p><p>苹果的 MagSafe 充电器配件售价 39 美元（尽管我们已经见过它打折好几次了），但如果你想少花一点钱， <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAW7_RLl0A0JotuPt2TK6AQhpSeA4qI36-2JHt1G3f1jM&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSpigen-ArcField-Magnetic-Wireless-Compatible%2Fdp%2FB08K3YZ535">Spigen 的 25 美元 ArcField 磁性无线充电器</a>是一个不错的选择。它的磁铁远不如 Apple MagSafe 充电器上的磁铁强——所以你<em>绝对</em>不应该通过这条电缆拿起你的 iPhone——但它会为你的手机供电并在这样做时保持原样。</p><h2> Mophie 四合一无线充电垫</h2><p><core-commerce id="6edfc614874b47caa801fe562bc2b9f7" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>此时您可能已经积累了许多支持无线充电的设备，而<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9XaXJlbGVzcy1DaGFyZ2luZy1tYXQtd2lyZWxlc3NseS1BZGRpdGlvbmFsL2RwL0IwOExLR1FMUkM_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZWEtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjYyN2FmM2ZkLTU5NGItMzE3OS04YzEzLWJhZGYzOTQwOTBjMCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAchYGzRJBwZ2OOHfeLdJan63LYTk2jS-gtduRrOAuBul&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FWireless-Charging-mat-wirelessly-Additional%2Fdp%2FB08LKGQLRC">Mophie 的 4 合 1 充电垫</a>是为所有这些设备供电的简单方法。它是一个 11 x 8 英寸的矩形，有四个空间，可供不同的物品同时充电。其中两个位置足够大，可以容纳智能手机，而中间的另外两个位置较小，可以完美容纳 AirPods 等设备。它还具有适用于 Apple Watch 的可选附件，这意味着它实际上可以同时为最多五台设备充电。</p><p>我发现这款垫子作为充电中心很有用，每天晚上都会用它来为我的 iPhone、Apple Watch 和 AirPods Pro 充电。值得注意的是，我的 iPhone 和 AirPods Pro 都装在保护套中，我无需将其中任何一个取下即可使用 Mophie 的垫子为它们充电。虽然垫子的尺寸允许它同时做很多事情，但找到足够大的地方来放置它也很困难。它适合大多数床头柜，但您可能需要先重新安排东西。 Mophie 拥有一个<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAT46VUufj25sSGTR9Yr5BxausC-Ai1oAEntGuZcpGELr&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FMophie-Wireless-Charge-Pad-Charging%2Fdp%2FB07XPWD4WW">三合一无线充电站</a>，占用空间更少，并为您的 iPhone、Apple Watch 和 AirPods 提供专用充电位置。</p><h2> AirPods </h2><p><core-commerce id="e58893eae71e42ddacd6b18f2709315d" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>现在众所周知， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:5;pos:1;pdid:AirPods" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAVbI8OmCpcR3dbzgtzUruvlocsC4j7956tYlas02ezwX&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-MME73AM-A-AirPods-3rd-Generation%2Fdp%2FB09JQL3NWT%3FlinkCode%3Dsl1%26linkId%3D079659e14da0db61111282bba7d20838%26language%3Den_US%26ref_%3Das_li_ss_tl" data-demonetize-referrer="https://amzn.to/3p6Vfq0" class="rapid-with-clickid">Apple AirPods</a>是 iPhone 用户的最佳无线耳机。苹果公司推出第三代型号，使其标准<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-airpods-review-2021-160026883.html">AirPods</a>变得更好，该型号具有改进的设计、明显更好的声音和更长的电池寿命。我们很欣赏新的“轮廓”设计，它比以前的 AirPods 舒适得多，而且 H1 芯片组使免提 Siri 以及快速配对和切换等功能成为可能。它们的 179 美元价格非常值得，但如果这对您来说有点贵， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:7;pos:1;pdid:Beats’ new Studio Buds" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9CZWF0cy1TdHVkaW8tQ2FuY2VsbGluZy1FYXJidWRzLUJ1aWx0LUJsdWV0b290aC1IZWFkcGhvbmVzL2RwL0IwOTZTVjhTSkc_&amp;signature=AQAAAfXH42cJpoPMZBO0iXMtLEJ2DIT9y_9qCa5TeJUcXpk1&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FBeats-Studio-Cancelling-Earbuds-Built-Bluetooth-Headphones%2Fdp%2FB096SV8SJG%3Fcrid%3D2ZXRDVSJ6W431%26keywords%3Dbeats%2Bstudio%2Bbuds%26qid%3D1638284111%26qsid%3D144-0249316-3122912%26sprefix%3Dbeats%2Bstudi%252Caps%252C162%26sr%3D8-3%26sres%3DB096SV8SJG%252CB098TV6MSG%252CB09JL41N9C%252CB085292V2M%252CB08C4KWM9T%252CB08CJCTG6Z%252CB0858MZFBC%252CB098V1GRL3%252CB08J3Y4W5J%252CB082Y214W3%252CB07YVYZ8T5%252CB094C4VDJZ%252CB088NGD49M%252CB08KDX5H5Z%252CB0857JQFYP%252CB0828BJGD2%26srpt%3DHEADPHONES%26linkCode%3Dsl1%26linkId%3De3c10d94537ac289bbad82b2117f15b0%26language%3Den_US%26ref_%3Das_li_ss_tl" data-demonetize-referrer="https://amzn.to/31aH5Me" class="rapid-with-clickid">Beats 的新款 Studio Buds</a>是一个<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/beats-studio-buds-review-150014566.html">不错的选择</a>。它们售价 150 美元，内置相同的 H1 芯片，声音均衡，但不会牺牲 Beats 设备闻名的强劲低音。</p><h2> Anker Nano II 45W 氮化镓充电器</h2><p><core-commerce id="a3c7cbf8efc14487b67b2c95b80b0b37" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>虽然 Apple 的 20W 充电器工作得很好，但您可以在<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9DaGFyZ2VyLUFua2VyLUFkYXB0ZXItU3VwcG9ydGVkLUZvbGRhYmxlL2RwL0IwOFQ1UVZUS1c_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZWEtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjYyN2FmM2ZkLTU5NGItMzE3OS04YzEzLWJhZGYzOTQwOTBjMCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAXqwEi4VrcOvVqQEVCnlChGkxWfR9E0tzmcmdoGx5pyn&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FCharger-Anker-Adapter-Supported-Foldable%2Fdp%2FB08T5QVTKW">Anker 的 Nano II 45W 充电器</a>中选择更通用的适配器。它不仅可以为 iPhone 快速充电，还可以全速为 2020 款 MacBook Air 以及 iPad 等中型设备充电。它比其他 45W 充电器小 34%，并采用 GaN 技术来防止过热。我们还赞赏它的插脚可以向下翻转，使适配器在您需要携带它旅行时更加紧凑。 45W 型号的价格为 40 美元，但 Anker 还提供<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAZOv8yJTgqAHSGR4grBSnXNhkAI2QIqOhExZd7ypEDFX&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FCharger-Anker-Adapter-Compact-Foldable%2Fdp%2FB091DS2M8X">30W 版本</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9Bbmtlci1DaGFyZ2VyLVBvd2VyUG9ydC1BZGFwdGVyLUZvbGRhYmxlL2RwL0IwOTVUUlYyNEI_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZWEtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjYyN2FmM2ZkLTU5NGItMzE3OS04YzEzLWJhZGYzOTQwOTBjMCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAARwY1Aj2-0bXZ1KLGKL3Ttc4y1GnT90MJUyFatXtrfbq&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FAnker-Charger-PowerPort-Adapter-Foldable%2Fdp%2FB095TRV24B">65W 双端口型号</a>，供您同时为手机和笔记本电脑充电时使用。</p><h2>航空标签</h2><p><core-commerce id="4749b99682564306a274eac125ffc12b" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> Apple 的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:12;pos:1;pdid:AirTags" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9BcHBsZS1NWDUzMkFNLUEtQWlyVGFnL2RwL0IwOTMzQlZLNlQ_dGg9MSZsaW5rQ29kZT1zbDEmbGlua0lkPWI2M2JmMDNkZmIxZjIzMmFjODc2NmFjMzU1NjRjNGVmJmxhbmd1YWdlPWVuX1VTJnJlZl89YXNfbGlfc3NfdGwmdGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZWEtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjYyN2FmM2ZkLTU5NGItMzE3OS04YzEzLWJhZGYzOTQwOTBjMCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAV5Upwrg9Ol3xadDhbM2G7axR0Jzf903z0oSOhGvTBaq&amp;gcReferrer=